<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink341">
<l>avarō vārār tāṉvan taṉṟē</l>
<l>kuyiṟpeṭai iṉkura lakava</l>
<l>vayirkkēḻ nuṇṇaṟa ṉuṭaṅkum poḻutē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Won’t he himself come? The season has arrived, </l>
<l>when bright tiny streamlets tremble in the sand </l>
<l>as female cuckoo calls for [its male friend] in sweet voice. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
